Command> glab ci ci lint

TL;DR> Use .gitlab-ci.yml in the current directory

Keywords> gitlab
        > ci

Example01> glab ci lint
Example02> glab ci lint .gitlab-ci.yml
Example03> glab ci lint path/to/.gitlab-ci.yml

Reference> https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/cli/-/blob/main/docs/source/ci/ci/lint.md
         > https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/cli/-/blob/main/docs/source/ci/lint.md
